description: "index.ts hardcoded version 0.1.0 while package.json/manifest are 2026.6.3; set to 2026.6.3. Add the two missing capability demos: registerVectorStoreAdapter (ts-starter-memory in-memory adapter) and registerFlags (--ts-starter-tag on native list). Expand hooks from 2 to all 5 (beforeCommand/afterCommand/onWrite/onRead/onIndex). Replace the incorrect test mock (registerHook/registerSchema do not exist in the SDK) with the real full ExtensionApi surface and assert every register*/hook fires. Add a comment explaining the defineExtension typed identity helper + type-only import / zero-runtime-coupling pattern. Reconcile README+manifest 8->9 capabilities with accurate names. Fix misnumbered section headers."
